rts and terminals the base metals segment includes the production and extraction of nonferrous minerals and are presented as nickel and its byproducts ferronickel copper gold precious metals and others and copper copper concentrated the others segment comprises sales and expenses of other products services and investments in joint ventures and associate in other business its subsidiaries include companhia portuaria da baia de sepetiba mineracao corumbaense reunida sa salobo metais sa vale international sa vale mocambique sa and vale oman pelletizing company llc » full overview of valen company address vale sa av graca aranha   andar crio de janeiro      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation gueitiro matsuo genso  murilo pinto de oliveira ferreira  fernando jorge buso gomes  luciano siani pires  rogerio nogueira  » more officers  directors vale sa news miner vale to look toward copper after secondquarter miss jul   update miner vale to look toward copper after ndquarter miss jul   vale ceo says hopes to reach  billion in net debt in  jul   vale ceo says hopes to reach  bln in net debt in  jul   brazils vale to cut capex eyes net debt goal of under  bln jul   » more valen news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialssteel